Invocation Name: dino facts
des:
Ask for Dinosaur Facts, and learn about what really matters, like dark matter.

Dinosaur Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Dinosaur Facts" or "Alexa, open Dinosaur Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
